{
  "name": "Necrotic Miasma",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "steam.png",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A sickly dark essence descends on a creature within range that you can see. The target must succeed a Dex\u0002terity saving throw or take <span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">[[/r 1d8]]</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\"> necrotic damage. </span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">The target gains no benefit from cover on this saving throw. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">The spell’s damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level </span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">[[/r 2d8]]</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">, 11th level </span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">[[/r 3d8]]</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">, and 17th level </span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">[[/r 4d8]]</span><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-primary);font-size:var(--font-size-14)\">. </span></p>",
